data.description: This Ideal Florida Home boasts 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, with a versatile floor plan that could easily convert it into a 4-bedroom haven. As you step through the front door, you're greeted by a spacious 12x12 ceramic tiled foyer leading to a modern kitchen with custom Virginia Elm floating shelves and stainless steel appliances. The space is illuminated by new kitchen lighting, complementing its contemporary design. A Florida room bathed in natural light awaits beyond the kitchen, ideal for relaxation or entertainment, and could easily serve as an additional bedroom. The primary bedroom features an ensuite bathroom for a private retreat, while the second bedroom adds its own unique charm. Step outside to a fenced backyard oasis with a screened-in pool and covered front porch. Other features include a new front storm door, a roof and HVAC system less than 5 years old, and an oversized garage with utility sink and storage. Furnishings are negotiable. Don't miss this opportunity to own a piece of paradise in a prime location! Buyer or buyers agent to verify all measurements.
